<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 00:59:04 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>朝鲜指责美国和韩国飞行间谍飞机和船只</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-accuses-us-south-korea-flying-spy-planes-ships-2024-05-25/</link><description>官方媒体朝中社周日称，朝鲜国防部指责美国和韩国加强朝韩边境周围的侦察活动，并警告称，如果其主权和安全受到侵犯，朝鲜将采取行动。</description><pubDate>Sat, 25 May 2024 22:36:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-accuses-us-south-korea-flying-spy-planes-ships-2024-05-25/</guid></item><item><title>意大利部长表示欧盟应效仿美国对中国商品征收关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/eu-should-follow-us-tariffs-over-chinese-goods-italy-minister-says-2024-05-25/</link><description>意大利工业部长阿道夫·乌尔索周六表示，欧盟应效仿美国，通过对中国产品征收关税来保护其工业。</description><pubDate>Sat, 25 May 2024 16:28:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/eu-should-follow-us-tariffs-over-chinese-goods-italy-minister-says-2024-05-25/</guid></item><item><title>耶伦表示，在俄罗斯的欧洲银行面临“巨大风险”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/european-banks-russia-face-awful-lot-risk-yellen-says-2024-05-25/</link><description>美国财政部长珍妮特·耶伦告诉路透社，欧洲银行在俄罗斯经营面临着越来越大的风险，美国正在考虑加强对被发现为俄罗斯战争活动提供交易援助的银行的二级制裁。</description><pubDate>Sat, 25 May 2024 15:31:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/european-banks-russia-face-awful-lot-risk-yellen-says-2024-05-25/</guid></item><item><title>美国国务院表示，美国对中国在台湾海峡的军事演习“深感关切”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-deeply-concerned-over-china-military-drills-taiwan-strait-state-dept-says-2024-05-25/</link><description>北京表示，这些演习是对台湾新总统周一就职演说的“惩罚”。</description><pubDate>Sat, 25 May 2024 15:28:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-deeply-concerned-over-china-military-drills-taiwan-strait-state-dept-says-2024-05-25/</guid></item><item><title>欧洲央行行长帕内塔表示，对于降息必要性的共识日益增强</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/ecbs-panetta-says-consensus-growing-need-rate-cut-2024-05-25/</link><description>欧洲央行政策制定者法比奥·帕内塔周六表示，由于通胀正在减弱，欧洲央行内部越来越一致认为有必要首次降息，从而为放松货币政策创造了条件。</description><pubDate>Sat, 25 May 2024 14:10:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/ecbs-panetta-says-consensus-growing-need-rate-cut-2024-05-25/</guid></item><item><title>耶伦表示乌克兰贷款计划得到支持，但还需要做更多工作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/yellen-says-ukraine-loan-plan-has-support-more-work-needed-2024-05-25/</link><description>该计划将探索如何利用约 3000 亿美元俄罗斯冻结资产的未来收入来帮助乌克兰。</description><pubDate>Sat, 25 May 2024 13:47:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/yellen-says-ukraine-loan-plan-has-support-more-work-needed-2024-05-25/</guid></item><item><title>欧洲央行帕内塔称意大利银行必须退出俄罗斯</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/italian-banks-must-quit-russia-ecbs-panetta-says-2024-05-25/</link><description>欧洲央行政策制定者法比奥·帕内塔周六表示，意大利银行必须停止在俄罗斯的业务，因为留在俄罗斯也会带来“声誉问题”。</description><pubDate>Sat, 25 May 2024 12:20:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/italian-banks-must-quit-russia-ecbs-panetta-says-2024-05-25/</guid></item><item><title>埃文斯在上海夺冠，卡西迪保持电动方程式领先</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/formula1/evans-wins-shanghai-cassidy-retains-formula-e-lead-2024-05-25/</link><description>新西兰车手米奇·埃文斯 (Mitch Evans) 周六在上海赢得了两场电动方程式比赛中的第一场，他的捷豹车队庆祝了过去四场比赛中的第三场胜利。</description><pubDate>Sat, 25 May 2024 11:12:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/formula1/evans-wins-shanghai-cassidy-retains-formula-e-lead-2024-05-25/</guid></item><item><title>从叛逆者到囚犯和左翼拉丁美洲偶像，佩佩·穆吉卡 (Pepe Mujica) 反思</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/rebel-prisoner-leftist-latin-american-icon-pepe-mujica-reflects-2024-05-25/</link><description>何塞·穆希卡曾经是一名游击队员、囚犯，后来成为乌拉圭总统，他巩固了自己作为拉丁美洲左翼偶像的地位，他坚称自己首先是一名农民和自然爱好者。</description><pubDate>Sat, 25 May 2024 11:02:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/rebel-prisoner-leftist-latin-american-icon-pepe-mujica-reflects-2024-05-25/</guid></item><item><title>七国集团同意为乌克兰提供进一步融资，并将在未来几周内讨论细节</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/g7-agree-further-financing-ukraine-discuss-details-coming-weeks-2024-05-25/</link><description>德国财政部长克里斯蒂安·林德纳周六表示，七国集团富裕民主国家的财政部长已就为乌克兰提供进一步融资达成一致，但尚未就细节达成一致。</description><pubDate>Sat, 25 May 2024 10:39:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/g7-agree-further-financing-ukraine-discuss-details-coming-weeks-2024-05-25/</guid></item><item><title>在动荡的新喀里多尼亚，马克龙看到了太平洋的力量和影响力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/restive-new-caledonia-macron-sees-pacific-power-influence-2024-05-25/</link><description>法国在印太地区的野心在经历了数天的岛屿骚乱后面临最严峻的考验。</description><pubDate>Sat, 25 May 2024 09:55:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/restive-new-caledonia-macron-sees-pacific-power-influence-2024-05-25/</guid></item><item><title>G7旨在利用冻结的俄罗斯资产帮助“绝望”的乌克兰</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/g7-will-try-use-frozen-russian-assets-help-ukraine-2024-05-25/</link><description>在莫斯科入侵邻国后不久，七国集团及其盟友冻结了约 3000 亿美元的俄罗斯金融资产。</description><pubDate>Sat, 25 May 2024 08:12:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/g7-will-try-use-frozen-russian-assets-help-ukraine-2024-05-25/</guid></item><item><title>中方指责英方对中国公民进行不实指控</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-accuses-uk-false-accusations-against-chinese-citizens-2024-05-25/</link><description>周六，一名被控非法协助香港外国情报部门的男子不明原因死亡，中国指责英国诬告、“肆意污名化”和任意逮捕。</description><pubDate>Sat, 25 May 2024 05:54:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-accuses-uk-false-accusations-against-chinese-citizens-2024-05-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国结束军演，台湾详细介绍战机和军舰增编</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-ends-war-games-taiwan-details-warplane-warship-surge-2024-05-25/</link><description>北京表示，这些演习是对台湾新总统就职演说的惩罚。</description><pubDate>Sat, 25 May 2024 02:20:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-ends-war-games-taiwan-details-warplane-warship-surge-2024-05-25/</guid></item><item><title>当地媒体报道，巴布亚新几内亚山体滑坡造成300多人被埋</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/more-than-300-buried-papua-new-guinea-landslide-local-media-says-2024-05-25/</link><description>据美国广播公司报道，山体滑坡堵塞了高速公路通道，直升机成为到达该地区的唯一途径。</description><pubDate>Sat, 25 May 2024 01:46:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/more-than-300-buried-papua-new-guinea-landslide-local-media-says-2024-05-25/</guid></item></channel></rss>